examples.en: The car crushed the toy.

examples.en: Peel and crush the garlic.

examples.en: Listen to criticism but don't be crushed by it.

examples.en: It's just a schoolgirl crush.

examples.en: The party isn't a crush. I have only asked about thirty odd people.

examples.en: The crush in the train station is at its worst during the afternoon rush hour.
examples.ru: Давка на вокзале хуже всего во второй половине дня, в час пик.

examples.en: The rocks were crushed into dust.

examples.en: It is common to make fun of schoolboy and schoolgirl "pashes" and "crushes".
examples.ru: Над школьными "увлечениями" и "страстями" принято посмеиваться.

examples.en: Crush two cloves of garlic.

examples.en: Their vehicle was crushed by an army tank.
examples.ru: Их машину раздавил боевой танк.

examples.en: There's always such a crush on the train in the mornings.
examples.ru: По утрам в поезде всегда такая давка.

examples.en: The cruel king crushed down any sign of opposition from the people.
examples.ru: Жестокий король подавлял малейшие попытки сопротивления в народе.

examples.en: Her bonnet and dress were all crushed.

examples.en: Crush the nuts and sprinkle them on top of the cake.

examples.en: Two people were crushed to death in the rush to escape.

examples.en: Any one of that crush would do murder for no more than 500 dollars reward.

examples.en: The military operation was the first step in a plan to crush the uprising.
examples.ru: Эта военная операция была первой в серии действий по подавлению восстания.

examples.en: If you walk in the farmer's field, be careful not to crush down any growing crops.

examples.en: When the gates of the ground were opened, crowds of football supporters crushed in.

examples.en: Use this kitchen machine to crush the juice out instead of pressing the fruit by hand.

examples.en: He sank upon a seat, almost crushed with the knowledge of the consequences of his action.
examples.ru: Он упал на скамейку, почти раздавленный мыслью о последствиях своего поступка.

examples.en: Her arm was crushed in the accident.

examples.en: His leg was crushed in the accident.
examples.ru: В этой аварии ему раздробило ногу.

examples.en: She was crushed by his refusal of her invitation.

examples.en: The bicycle was crushed under the truck's tires.
examples.ru: Велосипед был раздавлен колёсами грузовика.
